{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/refresh-atheme-vertical-thumbnails-with-arrow-navigation-on-product-pages-no-apps","result":{"pageContext":{"id":2166,"date":"2023-01-25T20:51:24","date_gmt":"2023-01-25T20:51:24","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=2166"},"modified":"2023-06-05T22:11:50","modified_gmt":"2023-06-05T22:11:50","slug":"refresh-atheme-vertical-thumbnails-with-arrow-navigation-on-product-pages-no-apps","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/refresh-atheme-vertical-thumbnails-with-arrow-navigation-on-product-pages-no-apps/","title":{"rendered":"Refresh theme: vertical thumbnails with arrow navigation on product pages [no apps]Â "},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Refresh is an extremely popular free theme developed by Shopify that excels at making a strong impression on viewers thought a modern and high customizable design combined with a cool color pallet that is pleasant to the eyes without being distracting. <br><br>It&#8217;s an excellent choice for store owners who wants to develop a strong brand identity and allow their clients to focus on the products they sell, which is why it&#8217;s unfortunate that the product page navigation is bland and requires lots of needless scrolling that might bore clients away from a purchase.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That can be fixed by hiring a professional developer to customize the product page for your store, but it&#8217;s not a perfect solution: coding can be a long and expensive process with lots of trial and error as your programmer tries to create the perfect design for you and your store. <br><br>Instead, our Slider Pro is a fully coded and tested snippet that&#8217;s easy to install even with no prior coding knowledge, giving you access to improved navigation in the product page with the following features:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Image thumbnails neatly stacked in a vertical, scrollable column. All you need to see in one place!</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Smart image gallery: open a different picture and the column scrolls by itself. It even loops around!</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Arrow icons, browse back and forth between images with a single click.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Alternate horizontal navigation scheme with dots replacing thumbnails, perfect for more minimalist designs.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re not convinced yet you can see it working live in our demo store <a href=\"https://refresh-password-is-123.myshopify.com/products/flex-bag\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">here</a> (<strong>password: 123</strong>) before learning how to install it below.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-making-a-backup-of-your-theme\">Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-downloading-the-files\">Downloading the files</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/refresh-theme-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>Download </strong>the files by clicking here.</a> (<a href=\"https://refresh-password-is-123.myshopify.com//products/flex-bag\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">live preview</a>)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-step-1-inserting-the-top-code\">Step 1: inserting the &#8220;top&#8221; code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>In your Shopify admin, click in order:&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1254\" height=\"367\" class=\"wp-image-2238\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/refresh-edit-code.png\" alt=\"Opening the code editor in the refresh theme\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/refresh-edit-code.png 1254w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/refresh-edit-code-850x249.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/refresh-edit-code-1200x351.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/refresh-edit-code-768x225.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1254px) 100vw, 1254px\" /><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Search for the following in the seach bar:<br><br><strong>main-product.liquid</strong><br><br>And open the file that&#8217;ll show up.<br> <br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"872\" height=\"632\" class=\"wp-image-1562\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1.jpg 872w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1-850x616.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1-768x557.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 872px) 100vw, 872px\" /><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>You&#8217;ll find a file called <strong>top.txt</strong> inside the .zip you downloaded. Copy all of the code inside it.<br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Paste it at the very start of the <strong>main-product.liquid</strong> file. Use the images below as reference. <br><br>Before:<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1092\" height=\"642\" class=\"wp-image-1566\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2.jpg 1092w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2-850x500.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2-768x452.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1092px) 100vw, 1092px\" /><br><br>After:<br></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1171\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1817\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-4.png 1171w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-4-850x441.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-4-768x399.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1171px) 100vw, 1171px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Step 2: inserting the &#8220;bottom&#8221; code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Still in the <em>&#8220;main-product.liquid&#8221;</em> file, open the search bar by pressing CTRL + F (or CMD + F on Mac) and type or paste in the following:<br><br><strong>{% schema</strong><br><br>Make sure the space after the % is there.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1277\" height=\"733\" class=\"wp-image-1568\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4.jpg 1277w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4-850x488.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4-1200x689.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4-768x441.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1277px) 100vw, 1277px\" /><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Now delete everything <strong>below </strong>the {% schema %} line including that very same line.<strong> </strong><br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1134\" height=\"730\" class=\"wp-image-1570\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5.jpg 1134w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5-850x547.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5-768x494.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1134px) 100vw, 1134px\" /><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Again in the .zip you downloaded, you&#8217;ll find a file called <strong>bottom.txt</strong>. <br><br>Copy its contents and paste them at the very end of the file.<br></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"580\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-5-1200x580.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1819\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-5-1200x580.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-5-850x411.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-5-768x371.png 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-5.png 1367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s all! Now all you need to do is customize your image navigation.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-final-step-activating-the-slider-and-customizing-it\">Final step: activating the slider and customizing it</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Starting from your Shopify admin, navigate through&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt; <strong>Customize</strong>. Make sure you&#8217;re choosing the Refresh theme you were just working on.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1248\" height=\"349\" class=\"wp-image-2255\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/refresh-customize.png\" alt=\"Opening the customization in the refresh theme\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/refresh-customize.png 1248w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/refresh-customize-850x238.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/refresh-customize-1200x336.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/refresh-customize-768x215.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1248px) 100vw, 1248px\" /><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>At the top of the page open the dropdown menu and select <strong>Products </strong>&gt; <strong>default product</strong>. <br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"928\" height=\"431\" class=\"wp-image-2353\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/refresh-product.png\" alt=\"Opening the product page in the Refresh theme\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/refresh-product.png 928w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/refresh-product-850x395.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/refresh-product-768x357.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 928px) 100vw, 928px\" /><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>In the new page, click on <strong>Product Information</strong> in the menu to the left.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"655\" height=\"558\" class=\"wp-image-2355\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/refresh-information.png\" alt=\"Opening the product information in the Refresh theme\"><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Scroll down until you find the <strong>Media </strong>section and choose the display option that you want. We&#8217;ll pick vertical thumbnails for this tutorial:<br></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"418\" height=\"528\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1821\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-conclusion\">Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope you enjoy your new vertical thumbnails and all other improvements brought by our Slider Pro! And if there were any issues during installation just contact us at <strong>ezfycode@gmail.com</strong> with your website URL and on the same day we&#8217;ll get back to you ready to help with everything you need. You may also want to check out out 